<h1>Cursor vs Copilot vs Claude Code Cost</h1>
<p class="updated" style="color:#6B7689;font-size:14px;margin-top:-6px">Updated 12 July 2026</p>
<p>Compare subscription pricing, credit value, and total cost of ownership for AI coding assistants. We break down Cursor, GitHub Copilot, and Claude Code by plan tier and show cost-per-day metrics to help you choose.</p>

<ul class="badge-row">
  <li>All pricing current as of July 2026</li>
  <li>Monthly subscription costs verified from official sources</li>
  <li>Credit value shows model access cost per dollar</li>
  <li>No annual discounts found for any vendor</li>
</ul>

